3.1 Numeric Dataset Description
Stock Market Data:
Source: Yahoo Finance (yfinance Python library).
Companies: AAPL, MSFT, GOOG, AMZN, and META.
Period: January 2018 â€“ January 2025.
Type: Collected automatically using Python scripts.
  
3.2 Text Modality Description
News Sentiment Data:
Source: NewsAPI.org (public API for real-time and historical news).
News Titles and Descriptions were fetched and analyzed for sentiment.
Each news record was timestamped to align with the corresponding stock data date.
